                <h1>&#039;Holy Moly!&#039;: Duke grads found cannoli food truck</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/7d9bb947-5e5a-4796-9fd9-4ad42de6f2d8.sized-1000x1000.jpeg?w=1000" alt="Michael&#x20;and&#x20;Christina&#x20;Steigerwald&#x20;founded&#x20;Holy&#x20;Moly&#x20;Cannoli&#x20;food&#x20;truck,&#x20;which&#x20;serves&#x20;a&#x20;variety&#x20;of&#x20;rotating&#x20;cannoli&#x20;flavors.&#x20;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Michael and Christina Steigerwald founded Holy Moly Cannoli food truck, which serves a variety of rotating cannoli flavors. 

